full_text: Screened by NARA, 7/21/2023 Part 4. Information about you. residences and employment. A. List your addresses during the last five (5) years or since you became a permanent resident, whichever IS less. Begin with your current address. If you need more space, continue on separate paper: Street Number and Name, City, State, Country, and Zip Code Dates (month/day/year) From To 3142 VERA AVENUE LOS ANGELES CALIFORNIA 90034 11-18-92 PRESENT 4 No others B. List your employers during the last five (5) years. List your present or most recent employer first. If none, write "None" If you need more space, continue on separate paper. Part 6. Information about your children. B. Total Number of Children 2 Complete the following information for each of your children. If the child lives with you, state "with me" in the address column; otherwise give city/state/country of child's current residence.
